{"tid":113964,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲睇過《香港文學》呢本雜誌？","createTime":"2017-02-09T11:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T10:34:45.000Z","uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"212522418fcd56050ad67050dc33f031e2fbfc92","tid":113964,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"睇左《酒徒》之後就去買左本黎睇 <br />\n<br />\n睇左少少之後覺得麻麻 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲買過黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a930a7f1675e0ff8669e13a203f0f931e62d5c","tid":113964,"uid":32834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左《酒徒》之後就去買左本黎睇 <br />\n<br />\n睇左少少之後覺得麻麻 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲買過黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買字花或者聲韻詩刊啦<br />\n或者買聯合文學"},{"pid":"f32752933d23bd16ea2761325b2833be62d3f714","tid":113964,"uid":70459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"中學時期有睇開，字花同香港文學既散文好多都寫得太深了，每一篇都要用好多時間去諗，基本上唔係for新手睇。有睇開意識流小說或新詩先睇得明。文學做唔到雅俗共賞，整到變哂文字密碼咁根本就本末倒置。"},{"pid":"66f19d59b06a05813ef4f317b36300e79cab8ec6","tid":113964,"uid":32834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學時期有睇開，字花同香港文學既散文好多都寫得太深了，每一篇都要用好多時間去諗，基本上唔係for新手睇。有睇開意識流小說或新詩先睇得明。文學做唔到雅俗共賞，整到變哂文字密碼咁根本就本末倒置。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文學係藝術黎，正如睇畫睇唔明唔會叫畫家畫簡單點啦，如果想睇淺d，可以睇中學生文藝月刊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc04217c1f76c9b45e2e7d94094964350a598dc7","tid":113964,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇左《酒徒》之後就去買左本黎睇 <br />\n<br />\n睇左少少之後覺得麻麻 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲買過黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買字花或者聲韻詩刊啦<br />\n或者買聯合文學</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n字花都買左 還可以 但香港文學真係有啲失望 依一期係講智能電話 我覺得呢個題目已經有少少唔係與時並進 扣左分"},{"pid":"6b955aa49433dc1cf69313f1898b0d8d63d73705","tid":113964,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學時期有睇開，字花同香港文學既散文好多都寫得太深了，每一篇都要用好多時間去諗，基本上唔係for新手睇。有睇開意識流小說或新詩先睇得明。文學做唔到雅俗共賞，整到變哂文字密碼咁根本就本末倒置。</blockquote><br />\n 各花入各眼 加上呢本雜誌嘅market唔係大眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f945738857090937d6874af72d1186548bfd5843","tid":113964,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"前衛文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2522c3c65864dbb87557f852addeb92815b43910","tid":113964,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"巴打而家讀緊當代文學？"},{"pid":"04493e467dbe5780be2c562d455573590000975a","tid":113964,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打而家讀緊當代文學？</blockquote><br />\n冇 之不過咁啱睇左酒徒 就屎忽痕去買左本香港文學黎睇"},{"pid":"7301bd81336c1a7d41ee60eef17b6e8b442466e8","tid":113964,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前衛文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麥荷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3ed2cb7341cf3151b9a45904e3986a5e2a56fc","tid":113964,"uid":55296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"初頭都有買過吓嚟睇，但越嚟越強說愁，好造作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009185534648fd17857be14701e6c2f52513f433","tid":113964,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初頭都有買過吓嚟睇，但越嚟越強說愁，好造作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打幾時開始買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢本野都算生存得耐<br />\n<br />\n啱啱最新呢期真係顯得佢地有啲後知後覺"},{"pid":"a20d2703b79110210e8d18ee068a9561b532a1a3","tid":113964,"uid":32834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"其實都要睇巴打鍾意咩野風格同時代感既文學作品，酒徒當年係厲害，但就藝術高度而言，劉以鬯真係唔高，你睇佢其他小說就知。<br />\n其實香港文學呢本野由好耐之前，已經有係土共資金支援（而家唔知），當年香港作為共產同西方意識形態既鬥爭之地，中美各自都資助左好多媒體，只不過當時受老美資助既文學刊物，好早已經全部收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港文學基本上唔多年輕作者，老派作者關注同思維與年輕人不同，巴打自然未必睇得有共鳴啦"},{"pid":"74f31d0be9528efba7c4498060a7d4268653f645","tid":113964,"uid":4782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都要睇巴打鍾意咩野風格同時代感既文學作品，酒徒當年係厲害，但就藝術高度而言，劉以鬯真係唔高，你睇佢其他小說就知。<br />\n其實香港文學呢本野由好耐之前，已經有係土共資金支援（而家唔知），當年香港作為共產同西方意識形態既鬥爭之地，中美各自都資助左好多媒體，只不過當時受老美資助既文學刊物，好早已經全部收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港文學基本上唔多年輕作者，老派作者關注同思維與年輕人不同，巴打自然未必睇得有共鳴啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打睇落好有研究 <br />\n就呢一期而言 本雜誌真係唔啱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇其他本地作家嘅好書推薦下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbd0a922755f9f0763b933f5dfc67729ea2ef4b","tid":113964,"uid":17353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:38:02.000Z","msg":"之前寫過一篇酒徒既評論，登左係份唔出名既文學報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f93b6490ee22904601729583a2250889376e3c","tid":113964,"uid":32834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前寫過一篇酒徒既評論，登左係份唔出名既文學報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫評論好啊 巴打keep住寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f748fd5d9874dbd0528fa7549a3aec57bdc16d","tid":113964,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前寫過一篇酒徒既評論，登左係份唔出名既文學報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b249b53c8a99bfb1598522282f4336e63bbd24","tid":113964,"uid":32834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實都要睇巴打鍾意咩野風格同時代感既文學作品，酒徒當年係厲害，但就藝術高度而言，劉以鬯真係唔高，你睇佢其他小說就知。<br />\n其實香港文學呢本野由好耐之前，已經有係土共資金支援（而家唔知），當年香港作為共產同西方意識形態既鬥爭之地，中美各自都資助左好多媒體，只不過當時受老美資助既文學刊物，好早已經全部收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港文學基本上唔多年輕作者，老派作者關注同思維與年輕人不同，巴打自然未必睇得有共鳴啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打睇落好有研究 <br />\n就呢一期而言 本雜誌真係唔啱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇其他本地作家嘅好書推薦下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打鍾意睇邊類，不過本地作家的話，小說試下睇黃碧雲、謝曉虹、韓麗珠、潘國靈、董啟章；<br />\n散文就睇吳煦斌、黃仁逵、李智良、淮遠<br />\n詩唔知巴打睇唔睇，就免講了"},{"pid":"1494c2a276ef36364bf275508d8aaa0ee0e28b8d","tid":113964,"uid":6208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"好有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請問邊到可以買到？"},{"pid":"e5ffa8690b2ecedec0842f40757c327096ad1225","tid":113964,"uid":45078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a978b4e9b2258f14d1d716440fdfcd5dcf2c8c","tid":113964,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實都要睇巴打鍾意咩野風格同時代感既文學作品，酒徒當年係厲害，但就藝術高度而言，劉以鬯真係唔高，你睇佢其他小說就知。<br />\n其實香港文學呢本野由好耐之前，已經有係土共資金支援（而家唔知），當年香港作為共產同西方意識形態既鬥爭之地，中美各自都資助左好多媒體，只不過當時受老美資助既文學刊物，好早已經全部收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港文學基本上唔多年輕作者，老派作者關注同思維與年輕人不同，巴打自然未必睇得有共鳴啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打睇落好有研究 <br />\n就呢一期而言 本雜誌真係唔啱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇其他本地作家嘅好書推薦下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打鍾意睇邊類，不過本地作家的話，小說試下睇黃碧雲、謝曉虹、韓麗珠、潘國靈、董啟章；<br />\n散文就睇吳煦斌、黃仁逵、李智良、淮遠<br />\n詩唔知巴打睇唔睇，就免講了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面之中, 只睇過董啟章"},{"pid":"2c8b684c605320d0cdada4d6e6777ce058c0614c","tid":113964,"uid":17353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前寫過一篇酒徒既評論，登左係份唔出名既文學報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫評論好啊 巴打keep住寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無寫好耐啦，我本身讀英文，以前讀書有時間先寫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講起好可惜既係，香港今時今日更加容不下「嚴肅文學」，以前係某間傳統既出版社做過編輯intern，都要上高登搵網絡小說出版，點知一出就大賣<br />\n而一d文學散文就完全無人問津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}